Here's an example of how to create a responsive image:

```css
/* Base style */
body {
    margin: 0;
    padding: 0;
}

/* Responsive images */
img {
    max-width: 1200px; /* Adjust this value as needed */
    height: auto;
}
```

In this example, the `max-width` property sets the maximum width allowed

